{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3933c280fd","title":"周恩来给纪登奎汪东兴的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e580e56e45","index":0,"year":1972,"month":12,"day":18,"articleId":"3933c280fd"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3df4ae75e1","name":"干部和干部政策","type":"主题"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"fb776baaf9","name":"邓小平","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0985b09bd2","type":"title","text":"周恩来给纪登奎汪东兴的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3933c280fd"},{"id":"95c3ac8078","type":"paragraph","text":"昨晚主席面示，谭震林同志虽有一时错误（现在看来，当时大闹怀仁堂是林彪故意造成打倒一批老同志的局势所激成的），但还是好同志，应该让他回来。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3933c280fd"},{"id":"0cbc761832","type":"paragraph","text":"此事请你们二人商办，他在桂林摔伤了骨头，曾请韦国清同志注意帮他治好。王良恩同志了解其情况，可问他关于震林同志一家的近情。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3933c280fd"},{"id":"ec8d4275a0","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平同志一家曾要求做点工作，请你们也考虑一下，主席也曾提过几次。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3933c280fd"},{"id":"7f4c8702b0","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3933c280fd"},{"id":"df6abc97d2","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七二年十二月十八日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3933c280fd"}],"page":{"id":"f47886f4f9","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3933c280fd","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}